{
  "texts": [
    "M. Haberreiter is senior researcher at the Physical-Meteorological Observatorium Davos/World Radiation Center.",
    "Her research interests include all aspects of solar variability, radiative transfer in the solar atmosphere, Sun-Earth connection and the Earth Energy Imbalance.",
    "She is Co-I of EUI and SPICE onboard Solar Orbiter.",
    "Currently, she is president of the Swiss Society for Astrophysics and Astronomy (SSAA) and a member of the Swiss national SCOSTEP committee.",
    "Before that, she served as EGU Division President for Solar-Terrestrial Sciences.W."
  ]
}